text.tspan: the result is true only if both operands are true
"I need a new computer" and "I have the money"
so "I will buy a new computer"
THEN "I will buy a new computer"
"I need a new computer" but "I don't have the money"
so I won't buy a new one
"I don't need a new computer" even if "I have the money"
so I won't buy a new one
and "I don't have the money" anyway
so I won't buy a new one
